<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l6">beweıſet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . Vnd wölten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daʒ wır das </ab>
