<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l14">gut getrawen ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr gnade allcʒeıt </ab>
